{"tid":1301383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】婆婆錯把「飛機杯」當「保暖襪」 孫仔一見嚇呆：「係我嘅玩具」","createTime":"2019-07-09T15:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T18:00:41.000Z","uid":66271,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"052633bfe251471e28c76002f25f5e1c1511994d","tid":1301383,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"身為成年人，擁有情趣玩具實在無可厚非，惟現今成人玩具設計精美，一旦被人誤會可能因而鬧出笑話。日本一位婆婆就因覺雙腳發冷，誤將孫兒的粉紅色矽膠製自慰器當成保溫襪使用，更因玩具內側黏性太強，最終需由孫兒協助方將「襪子」除下，同時令孫子成為網民恥笑對象。<br />\n<br />\n自慰器當保暖襪 孫仔玩具「被盜」超尷尬<br />\n<br />\n日本一名21歲男網民日前將尷尬經歷上載Twitter。據悉事主與家人同住，日前婆婆因覺得雙腳發冷，故從事主房間取走一雙粉紅色的「保溫襪」並套在腳上取暖。<br />\n<br />\n事後婆婆向事主稱已將襪子借走一用，此話卻令事主大感奇怪，因事主根本沒有甚麼保暖襪。當他走入婆婆房間一看才發現腳上的粉紅色物體並非襪子，而是他用過的自慰器。從事主上傳照片可見，婆婆兩邊腳掌各穿一隻「襪子」，雖然前端呈半圓形略顯怪異，惟尺碼卻意外適中，甚至能夠包裹腳踭位置，看來確有保溫之效。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2395000/2395017/555_600.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2395000%2F2395017%2F555_600.PNG&h=af14f461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事主婆婆因感腳掌冰冷，故擅自取走孫兒「保暖襪」一用。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n彈性超強 孫兒出手幫「除襪」<br />\n<br />\n得悉錯著孫兒「玩具」的婆婆相當錯愕，想脫下之際才發現腳掌被「啜實」欲脫無門，事主遂出手幫忙，於另一邊使力狂拉。但因自慰器彈性太好加上內側黏性強勁，事主花相當大力氣才將自慰器成功拉出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2395000/2395017/22_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2395000%2F2395017%2F22_600.png&h=3d68c286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事主費盡九牛二虎之力方成功將「襪子」脫下。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n網民突破盲點：「難除因無加潤滑劑」<br />\n<br />\n面對如此遭遇，事主不禁於Twitter坦言「活了21年，沒想過有要從婆婆腳上拉走自慰器的一天...」。相關影片上載短短3日就錄得近350萬次瀏覽，並引來不少網民取笑。有人指婆婆雙腳被勒得通紅，指事主應該要加點潤滑劑而不應硬拉。亦有人指該玩具洞口應該相當狹窄，可以想像婆婆必然有極大決心方可將腳掌穿進去，建議事主應儘快為婆婆添置一雙厚襪子保暖。"},{"pid":"f4f69be8073eccb4283e27f23c30a52bd7e2985f","tid":1301383,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a387a4c801b0ad2ffe4b173ebc4abb8a93ad0e5a","tid":1301383,"uid":973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41dab82b182f841207923de56ed8e66fcf363ca","tid":1301383,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a387a4c801b0ad2ffe4b173ebc4abb8a93ad0e5a","tid":1301383,"uid":973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:34:31.000Z","msg":"呀婆識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e98d9a27c8ba7f9d5181e599553008160192a3d","tid":1301383,"uid":175976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"可能有香港腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ec2df3d75e826b370b19af50d4ba3950b17431","tid":1301383,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9903de7458b15c2e00bf8e947120695060f1f6","tid":1301383,"uid":197163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class